      "period": 24,
      "marker": true,
      "label": "10:30 \u2014 peak dependence",
      "text": "Firm power is at its daily low. Net imports peak near 6,900 MW and the wind fleet is delivering about a tenth of its plate. This is the standing exposure \u2014 hours before anything goes wrong."
    },
    {
      "period": 38,
      "marker": false,
      "label": "17:30 \u2014 the price turns",
      "text": "The settled price jumps to \u00a3317/MWh as the evening peak builds and solar fades."
    },
    {
      "period": 43,
      "marker": true,
      "label": "20:00 \u2014 the emergency",
      "text": "Demand peaks. Gas has ramped to cover and imports have withdrawn as neighbours keep their power. Firm plant is now carrying the country \u2014 the ~\u00a31,400/MWh emergency price is the market clearing that squeeze."
    }
